{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/make/robot/encyclopedia.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"tank-like-robot\" style=\"position:relative;\">Tank-like robot<a href=\"#tank-like-robot\" aria-label=\"tank like robot permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p>SMARS <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:2662828\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">version 1</a>, <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/smars-v4-lite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">version 4 (lite)</a> created by <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/users/Tuitxy/3d-models\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kevin Thomas</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.2635658914728682;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/7bf67/smars-v4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.14110429447852%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"smars v4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/6aca1/smars-v4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/d2f63/smars-v4.jpg 163w,\n/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/c989d/smars-v4.jpg 325w,\n/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/6aca1/smars-v4.jpg 650w,\n/static/1098c54ef20428ab1ff0c435b2608c45/7bf67/smars-v4.jpg 680w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I originally saved a link to <strong>Cults 3D</strong> where I saw similar interface to <strong>Thingeverse</strong> and the download button. But that doen't allow you to take the files. And then I noticed that in one year the creator has made 3000 euro selling this model by 5 euro for the zip. Looks like a good business model for hobby.</p>\n<p>But I'm a guy from Soviet Union, which means I am okay to spend some time and create my own version, because engineering is in my blood. Here's helpful <a href=\"https://www.smarsfan.com/learn/design/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">design walkthrough</a> from Kevin McAleer.</p>\n<p>Similar <a href=\"https://burariweb.info/electronic-work/mini-tank-esp8266.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">tank from Japan</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/smars-quad-mod\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Quad pod version</a> of SMARS. Compare with another small <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/kame-8dof-small-quadruped-robot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">quadruped robot</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"dog-like-robot\" style=\"position:relative;\">Dog-like robot<a href=\"#dog-like-robot\" aria-label=\"dog like robot permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 544px; flex:1.38135593220339;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7584bf134577fcdfe9790f10ef930ccd/72da7/robot-dog.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.39263803680981%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Small robot dog\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7584bf134577fcdfe9790f10ef930ccd/72da7/robot-dog.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7584bf134577fcdfe9790f10ef930ccd/d2f63/robot-dog.jpg 163w,\n/static/7584bf134577fcdfe9790f10ef930ccd/c989d/robot-dog.jpg 325w,\n/static/7584bf134577fcdfe9790f10ef930ccd/72da7/robot-dog.jpg 544w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 544px) 100vw, 544px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>From <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:5403752\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:5403752</a></p>\n<p>And <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/conveyor-for-ore-sorting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">similar dog</a> called by the creator: conveyor for ore sorting 🤣</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.7717391304347827;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/4b319/dog-robot-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"conveyor for ore sorting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/6aca1/dog-robot-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/d2f63/dog-robot-1.jpg 163w,\n/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/c989d/dog-robot-1.jpg 325w,\n/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/6aca1/dog-robot-1.jpg 650w,\n/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/7c09c/dog-robot-1.jpg 975w,\n/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/01ab0/dog-robot-1.jpg 1300w,\n/static/c11b9a403c20382ae9e7f02107acf3d8/4b319/dog-robot-1.jpg 5472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.7717391304347827;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/4b319/dog-robot-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"conveyor for ore sorting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/6aca1/dog-robot-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/d2f63/dog-robot-2.jpg 163w,\n/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/c989d/dog-robot-2.jpg 325w,\n/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/6aca1/dog-robot-2.jpg 650w,\n/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/7c09c/dog-robot-2.jpg 975w,\n/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/01ab0/dog-robot-2.jpg 1300w,\n/static/1ed5b9e158e58a197a4c6ebd479a17c0/4b319/dog-robot-2.jpg 5472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"kawaii-robot\" style=\"position:relative;\">Kawaii robot<a href=\"#kawaii-robot\" aria-label=\"kawaii robot permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/471c919ea986f279e37985921ca5d2a7/stack-chan-robot-owl.gif\" alt=\"Stack-chan owl\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hackaday.io/project/181344-stack-chan-javascript-driven-super-kawaii-robot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stack-chan</a> robots created by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/meganetaaan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shinya Ishikawa</a> and its community. For example <a href=\"https://protopedia.net/prototype/3299\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">this</a> sad yellow lizard by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KantenNamako\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Namako</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; flex:1.3583333333333334;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35b2639cb9f01f05763b33d9d4fdd4f1/0b533/robot-sad-yellow-lizard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.61963190184049%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sad yellow lizard\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/35b2639cb9f01f05763b33d9d4fdd4f1/0b533/robot-sad-yellow-lizard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35b2639cb9f01f05763b33d9d4fdd4f1/222b7/robot-sad-yellow-lizard.png 163w,\n/static/35b2639cb9f01f05763b33d9d4fdd4f1/ff46a/robot-sad-yellow-lizard.png 325w,\n/static/35b2639cb9f01f05763b33d9d4fdd4f1/0b533/robot-sad-yellow-lizard.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>It has \"stack\" in it's name because it uses <a href=\"https://m5stack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">M5Stack</a> which is a tiny box 5 cm on the side with a screen based on very popular low-cost system on a chip - <strong>ESP32</strong>. I remember first hearing about M5 from <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v9sNzmtMSXo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube video reviewing</a> their <a href=\"https://shop.m5stack.com/products/m5paper-esp32-development-kit-comm-edition\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">E-ink display kit</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://protopedia.net/prototype/3277\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://protopedia.net/prototype/3277</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"bi-pedal\" style=\"position:relative;\">Bi-pedal<a href=\"#bi-pedal\" aria-label=\"bi pedal permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>cute <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/rofi-bipedal-robot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/gadget/rofi-bipedal-robot</a></li>\n<li>just a model, but impressing mech <a href=\"https://cults3d.com/en/3d-printing/heavy-armored-thicc-boi-of-brutality-dantheman223\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://cults3d.com/en/3d-printing/heavy-armored-thicc-boi-of-brutality-dantheman22